.

Fun Singles , was founded as a result of unmarried people looking for a singles social group that is involved in a variety of fun activities. Most of our members live in the Ma or NH. Fun Singles provides a wide range of activities for single adults as well as opportunities to meet new friends. The club was not formed as, and is NOT, a dating service. Fun Singles has no political or religious orientations. We are a group of single people that is member run and propelled by member involvement at member sponsored events.

If you like to run events or just want to help out we are looking for event host and organizers, please let me know if you want to help our meetup grow!

Thanks

Dana
